## ğŸ§° Template 3: Prompting AI to Reframe Tone (Empathy, Urgency, Calm)

**Use When:** The message is technically right, but emotionally off.

```
You are using AI to reframe tone â€” not facts â€” for a sensitive message.

Friction â†’ The current message feels robotic or sharp.  
Bridge â†’ AI can model emotional cues, but must be nudged.  
Evidence â†’ It helped soften transitions and rephrase hard lines.  
Implication â†’ Without human review, tone may still feel performative.  
Action â†’ Prompt AI: â€œRewrite with calm authority + reader-first perspective.â€  
Look Ahead â†’ Check final draft with 2 humans: 1 internal, 1 external if possible.
```

---

### âœ… Example 3

```
You are informing teams about a delayed product release.

Friction â†’ Original message read like a blame game.  
Bridge â†’ Prompted AI to use calm, empathetic framing with transparent reasoning.  
Evidence â†’ Resulting draft kept facts but removed accusatory tone.  
Implication â†’ Still had vague sections, which you tightened manually.  
Action â†’ Final note used AIâ€™s improved transitions but kept your CTA intact.  
Look Ahead â†’ Shared timeline will be revisited weekly with shared status updates.
```

