## ğŸš§ Where AI Fails in Messaging (Blockers)

| Issue Type             | What It Looks Like                                                  | Fix It With Flavor & Function                                        |
|------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------|
| âŒ Tone Blindness       | AI-generated output sounds polished but flat or tone-deaf            | Use **Bridge** and **Look Ahead** to humanize and sanity-check tone |
| âŒ Prompt Ambiguity     | Output varies wildly based on minor changes in instruction           | Use **Friction** and **Action** to shape clear prompting paths      |
| âŒ Hidden Assumptions   | AI fills in gaps with wrong or biased assumptions                    | Add **Evidence** step to ground in known truth                      |
| âŒ Hallucinated Help    | AI â€œadds valueâ€ that isnâ€™t fact-checked                              | Implication section must stress human review before trust           |

